tafsir[11]{c,v,t}:
  93,1,"Alla woondirii arwannde ñalawma."
  93,2,"Alla woondirii jemma si mbo niɓɓiɗi dille aade en deeƴi."
  93,3,"joom Ma -aan nelaaɗo- accaani Ma, O tikkanaani ma, hono no sirkuɓe mbi*irata nde wahyu darii setta."
  93,4,"Ko gelle laakar ɓuri galle aduna, sabu ko mbo soomi ko e neemaaji duumiiɗi ɗi taƴandirtah."
  93,5,"Yaama joom ma okku ma baraaje aan e leñol ma haa mbeleɗa ko O okku ma ko."
  93,6,"O tawii ma ko a yatiime mbo baaba mum sankii, O tottuma moolorde, Taane Abdul Muttalibi neh ma ko noon kadi Bappa ma Abuu Taalib."
  93,7,"O tawma a anndah binndol e iimaan, O anndin ma heen ko a anndaana."
  93,8,"O taw ma ko a baasɗo O alɗin ma."
  93,9,"Woto bonnu gollodde e alyatiima baasɗo baaba makko saanga cukaagu, woto hoynu mbo."
  93,10,"Woto furo ñaagatooɗo katajinɗo."
  93,11,"Yettu neema mbo joom ma neemin ma kaala mbo."
